<placeName cert="high">Karanis</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἰσιδώρα Σαραπιάδι τῇ θυ-

    <lb n="2"/>γατρὶ πολλὰ <space dim="horizontal" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>πρὸ μὲν πάντων εὔχομαί 

    <lb n="4"/><choice><corr>σε</corr><sic>σαι</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ὑγιαίνειν</corr><sic>υγειενιν</sic></choice> μετὰ τῶν σῶ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> 

    <lb n="5"/>καὶ τὸ προσκύνημά σου ποιῶ 

    <lb n="6"/>παρὰ τῷ <choice><corr>κυρίῳ</corr><sic>κυρειω</sic></choice> <choice><corr>Σεράπιδι</corr><sic>σεραπιδος</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="7"/>μετὰ τοῦ τέκνου σου. 

    <lb n="8"/><choice><corr>οἶδας</corr><sic>οιδες</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ὅτι</corr><sic>οτει</sic></choice> ἀθυμῶ <choice><corr>τῷ</corr><sic>το</sic></choice> <choice><corr>νῷ</corr><sic>νο</sic></choice> διὰ τὸν 

    <lb n="9"/>ἀδελφόν σου. οὐκ ἔλαβα αὐ-

    <lb n="10"/>τοῦ τὰ <choice><corr>δηπόσιτα</corr><sic>δηποσειτα</sic></choice> ὃτι ἠσθένη-

    <lb n="11"/>κα· ἡμέρας ἔχουσι <choice><corr>λαμβάνειν</corr><sic>λαμμανι<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied></sic></choice>. 

    <lb n="12"/><choice><corr>περὶ</corr><sic>περει</sic></choice> οὗ <choice><corr>εἴρηκας</corr><sic>ειρηχες</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ὅτι</corr><sic>οτει</sic></choice> πέμψον 

    <lb n="13"/><choice><corr>χιτῶνα</corr><sic>κειθωνα</sic></choice> τῇ <choice><corr>μικρᾷ</corr><sic>μεικκη</sic></choice>, <choice><corr>ἐὰν</corr><sic>ηαν</sic></choice> εὕ-

    <lb n="14"/>ρω <choice><corr>τινὰ</corr><sic>τεινα</sic></choice> <choice><corr>πιστὸν</corr><sic>πειστον</sic></choice> πέμψω. 

    <lb n="15"/>καὶ <choice><corr>ἐὰν</corr><sic>ηαν</sic></choice> ὁ θεὸς θέλῃ κατέλαβά σε. 

    <lb n="16"/>εἴ <choice><corr>τι</corr><sic>τει</sic></choice> ἔχω <choice><corr>σόν</corr><sic>σεν</sic></choice> ἐστιν καὶ τοῦ ἀδελ-

    <lb n="17"/>φοῦ σου. ἤκουσα <choice><corr>ὅτι</corr><sic>οτει</sic></choice> ἀηδίαν <choice><corr>πεποί-

    <lb n="18"/>ηκας</corr><sic>πεποιηκες</sic></choice> μετὰ τοῦ ἀνδρός σου χάριν τοῦ 

    <lb n="19"/>πατρός σου. οὐ <choice><corr>μεμένηκε</corr><sic>μεμενηκαι</sic></choice> ἐχόνο-

    <lb n="20"/>μά μου <choice><corr>ὅτι</corr><sic>οτει</sic></choice> χειμών ἐστιν. πέμ-

    <lb n="21"/>ψον αὐτὸν παρ᾽ αὑτόν· <choice><corr>ἐὰν</corr><sic>ηαν</sic></choice> ἀναβῶ 

    <lb n="22"/>κυβερνήσω αὐτ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὸ</supplied>ν πάλιν. μένω 

    <lb n="23"/>Ἀπολλῶν. <subst><add place="inline">τάχα</add><del rend="corrected"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">χ</unclear>αχα</del></subst> στρατεύσηται· 

    <lb n="24"/>στρατευθῇ μὴ σ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ</supplied>ρατευθῇ <choice><corr>δεῖ</corr><sic>δι</sic></choice> με 

    <lb n="25"/>ἀναβῆναι. γράψον <subst><add place="inline">μοι</add><del rend="corrected">μου</del></subst> περὶ τῆς 

    <lb n="26"/><choice><corr>σωτηρίας</corr><sic>σωτηρειας</sic></choice> σου ἐν τάχει. <choice><corr>ἐὰν</corr><sic>ηαν</sic></choice> θέλῃς 

    <lb n="27"/>γράψαι <choice><corr>ἐπιστολήν</corr><sic>επισστολειν</sic></choice> ἐχόνομα Σε-

    <lb n="28"/>ρήνου τοῦ ἀδελφοῦ <choice><corr>Σκαμβῦτος</corr><sic>σκαμβυτες</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="29"/>μένω τὸ προσκύνημα αὐτοῦ 

    <lb n="30"/><choice><corr>εἰς</corr><sic>ις</sic></choice> τὸν <choice><corr>κόλπον</corr><sic>κολφον</sic></choice> τοῦ <subst><add place="inline">Σεράπιδος</add><del rend="corrected">εεραπιδος</del></subst>. 

    <lb n="31"/>ἀσπάζου τὸν <choice><corr>πατέρα</corr><sic>πατεραν</sic></choice> <subst><add place="inline">τῶν</add><del rend="corrected">τον</del></subst> 

    <lb n="32"/><subst><add place="inline"><choice><corr>παιδίων</corr><sic>πεδιων</sic></choice></add><del rend="corrected">πεδιον</del></subst> καὶ τὰ παιδία. <choice><corr>ἀσπα-

    <lb n="33"/>σαι</corr><sic>ασπασε</sic></choice> Θαυσᾶριν <choice><corr>ἄσ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">πα</supplied>σαι</corr><sic>ασσε</sic></choice> τὰ τέκνα σου. 

    <lb n="34"/>ἀσπάζου Πεηοῦν καὶ Πεμέν. 

    <lb n="35"/>μὴ ἀναγκάσῃς μέ σε μέμψα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σ</supplied>-

    <lb n="36"/>θαί <choice><corr>σε</corr><sic>σαι</sic></choice> <choice><corr>Ὀννῶφριν</corr><sic>οννωφρειν</sic></choice> ἐπὶ <gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> ἀηδίᾳ 

    <lb n="37"/>αὐτῆς. <gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> ἀσπάζεταί <choice><corr>σε</corr><sic>σαι</sic></choice> Ἀπολ-

    <lb n="38"/>λῶς καὶ τὰ τέκνα σου. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="39"/><expan>ἀπό<ex cert="high">δος</ex></expan> <choice><corr>Ὀννῶφρι</corr><sic>οννω<g type="x"/>φρεις</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ἱερεῖ</corr><sic>ειερ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear>υς</sic></choice> <gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>α<gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ησ<gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><add place="supralinear">το</add> 

    <lb n="40"/>ἀπὸ <choice><corr>Ἀπολλῶτος</corr><sic>απολλω<g type="x"/>τος</sic></choice> Σα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λι</unclear>βωτ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ᾶ</unclear>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.30514" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.30514" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="300" notBefore="201" type="textDate">III</date></p></div><div n="meta.30514" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Mich.</title><biblScope type="volume">8</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">514</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">30514</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0163</series>; <biblScope type="volume">8</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">514</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0163;8;514" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.30514" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">Plate VIII</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.30514" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="en"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Bagnall - Cribiore, Women's Letters (2006), S. 269</bibl><bibl type="translations">Bagnall - Cribiore, Women's Letters (2008), B1.9, Nr. 146.</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="it"><head lang="de">Italienisch:</head><bibl type="translations">S. Daris, ANRW II, 10.1 (1988), S. 729 (Z. 1-11)</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.30514" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Alexandria</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.30514" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://wwwapp.cc.columbia.edu/ldpd/app/apis/item?mode=item&amp;key=michigan.apis.2554